title: Zoo
description:
Within is a boat load of every type of popular bestiality, videos, photos, and some stories for your enjoyment.

This is a Dropbox folder link that my friend gave to me awhile ago.
The amount of videos and photos are too big to be added to Dropbox and then download without upgrading your Dropbox account. So I took the liberty of downloading the whole thing.

The folder is in its original structure.
I had to put it in a zip due to the amount of files
